---
title: Dijon Onion Crunch Salmon over Lemony Broccoli Spaghetti
description: This restaurant-worthy crusted salmon is surprisingly easy to pull off. Brush the salmon with mustard, press on the melty Italian blend cheeses and (already) crispy fried onions, and simply pop it in the oven. When baked, the crust gets golden brown while the salmon stays juicy and tender. Add a lemony, extra creamy (see: cheese roux + cream cheese + garlic butter) broccoli spaghetti on the side and you are in for a flavor and texture extravaganza.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/dijon-onion-crunch-salmon-569ca9ca.jpg
